\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \left(\omega_{1}\left(\boldsymbol{\theta}\right),\ldots,\omega_{k}\left(\boldsymbol{\theta}\right):\boldsymbol{\theta}\in\Theta\right)\right\} $
