 & =I_{\left\{ \theta-\frac{1}{2}<x_{i}<\theta+\frac{1}{2}\right\} },
\end{flalign*}

\end_inset

so that the joint pdf of 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{X}=X_{1},\ldots,X_{n}$
\end_inset

 is given by
\begin_inset Formula 
