\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $c\in\left(0,1\right]$
\end_inset

, so that 
\begin_inset Formula $-2\log c\geq0$
\end_inset

, so that 
\begin_inset Formula $k=\sqrt{-2\log c}\geq0$
\end_inset

.
 Specify a size 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=0.05$
\end_inset

 test.
