\end_inset

Now, since 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi'$
\end_inset

 is a level 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

 test, 
\begin_inset Formula $\sup_{\theta\in\Theta_{0}}\beta'\left(\theta\right)=\beta'\left(\theta_{0}\right)\leq\alpha$
\end_inset

.
