\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Z=\frac{\bar{X}-\theta}{1/\sqrt{n}}\sim\mathcal{N}\left(0,1^{2}\right),
\]

\end_inset

we have
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{flalign*}
