 & =P\left(\left\{ \left|\theta_{0}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}Z-\theta_{1}\right|\geq\frac{1.96}{\sqrt{n}}\right\} \right)\\
 & =P\left(\left\{ \left|-\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}Z+\left(\theta_{0}-\theta_{1}\right)\right|\geq\frac{1.96}{\sqrt{n}}\right\} \right)\\
