\begin_inset Formula 
\[
c\geq\lambda\left(x\right)\implies\text{reject }H_{0}\text{ if }\begin{cases}
\frac{1}{2-2x}\leq c, & x<\frac{1}{2}\\
\frac{1}{2x}\leq c, & x>\frac{1}{2}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

for some 
\begin_inset Formula $c\in\left(0,1\right)$
\end_inset

.
 I.e., we will reject 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{0}$
\end_inset

