\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{2-2x}\leq c\implies1\leq c\left(2-2x\right)\implies\frac{1}{c}\leq2-2x\implies\frac{1}{c}-2\leq-2x\implies x\leq1-\frac{1}{2c}
\]

\end_inset

for 
\begin_inset Formula $x<\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

