\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{2x}\leq c\implies1\leq c\left(2x\right)\implies x\geq\frac{1}{2c}
\]

\end_inset

for 
\begin_inset Formula $x>\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

.
