\begin_inset Formula $f\left(\mathbf{x}^{\left(0\right)}\right)=6$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\nabla f\left(\mathbf{x}^{\left(0\right)}\right)=\left(1,1\right)$
\end_inset

.
