\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{x}^{*}$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{x}^{*}=\argmin_{\mathbf{x}}f\left(\mathbf{x}\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
We have 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
