\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{x}^{\left(0\right)}=\left(2,4\right)$
\end_inset

, so that 
\begin_inset Formula $\nabla f\left(\mathbf{x}^{\left(0\right)}\right)=\left(17,52\right)$
\end_inset

.
