3 & 2
\end{bmatrix}\implies f\left(\mathbf{x}\right)=\sum_{i=1}^{2}\sum_{j=1}^{2}x_{i}x_{j}a_{ij}=x_{1}^{2}\cdot1+x_{1}x_{2}\cdot3+x_{2}x_{1}\cdot3+x_{2}^{2}\cdot2=x_{1}^{2}+6x_{1}x_{2}+2x_{2}^{2}.
\]

\end_inset

We see that 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

